#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TNEF File Viewer is an application for <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/TNEF\">TNEF</ulink> mail attachments."
msgstr ""
"De TNEF-bestandsviewer is een toepassing voor <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/TNEF\">TNEF</ulink>-e-mailbijlagen."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
